.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This logging engine uses Test::More's \fBnote()\fR to output as \s-1TAP\s0 comments.
.PP
This is very useful in case you're writing a test and want to have logging
messages as part of your \s-1TAP.\s0
.PP
"Like \f(CW\*(C`diag()\*(C'\fR, except the message will not be seen when the test is run in a
harness. It will only be visible in the verbose \s-1TAP\s0 stream." \*(-- Test::More.
